FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773936669
OL,3,CBusinesses sign letter after plans to
OL,4,Cwithdraw funding from night-time
OL,5,Ceconomy
OL,7,FCouncillor Tom Renhard, the Labour
OL,8,FGroup Leader at Bristol City Council,
OL,9,Fsaid: "It certainly is a tough time
OL,10,Ffor everyone however I really believe
OL,11,Fin the role of local government as a
OL,12,Fconvening role.
OL,14,F"One of the things you can do as place
OL,15,Fleaders, as local politicians, is to
OL,16,Fbring people together to help tackle
OL,17,Fthose challenges head on to be a voice.
OL,26,@qD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773936669
OL,3,CBusinesses sign letter after plans to
OL,4,Cwithdraw funding from night-time
OL,5,Ceconomy
OL,7,F"I think it's very short-sighted that
OL,8,Fthe role is being scrapped. It's
OL,9,Fachieved a lot, it should be
OL,10,Fcontinuing in my view and if there are
OL,11,Fthings that we could do even better,
OL,12,Flet's have that conversation.
OL,14,F"I just think it's been so damaging."
OL,16,FBristol City Council intends to
OL,17,Fwithdraw its funding for the project
OL,18,Fby the end of the month but says the
OL,19,Fmoney will go towards other projects.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
