PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773936669
OL,3,CBusinesses sign letter after plans to
OL,4,Cwithdraw funding from night-time
OL,5,Ceconomy
OL,7,FIn a statement it said: "The initial
OL,8,Ftranche of funding for this work
OL,9,Fexpired in 2023. Since then, it was
OL,10,Fdecided to continue the work programme
OL,11,Funtil it had achieved many of its
OL,12,Foutcomes, with Public Health providing
OL,13,Fone-off funding, which concludes at
OL,14,Fthe end of March 2026.
OL,16,F"The passion and commitment reflected
OL,17,Fin your letter is valued, and it is
OL,18,Fclear that many people care deeply
OL,19,Fabout ensuring the city's nightlife
OL,20,Fcan thrive while remaining safe,
OL,21,Finclusive and sustainable.
OL,26,@oD@YOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
