FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773936669
OL,3,CBusinesses sign letter after plans to
OL,4,Cwithdraw funding from night-time
OL,5,Ceconomy
OL,7,F"Our recognition of your sector's
OL,8,Fvalue can be seen in the many years we
OL,9,Fhave worked together with partners to
OL,10,Fdeliver support for the night time
OL,11,Feconomy.
OL,13,F"This includes activities specifically
OL,14,Ftargeted towards people working within
OL,15,Fand enjoying Bristol's brilliant night
OL,16,Flife and hospitality, alongside
OL,17,Fsupport for the thousands of people
OL,18,Fthat work at night in other sectors,
OL,19,Fsuch as health, care, transport and
OL,20,Fretail."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU|D@HO]
